me": "3.png", "id": "379064010595825", "uri": "https://scontent-ams2-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031440_379064013929158_562566670393182718_n.png?_nc_cat=108&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=dIPkI2HTwUAQ7kNvgHkgdvu&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-ams2-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYC-hpzPKyK2fq7lr--kHwQRNyN679fj1nqmGWACcKkmRg&oe=677BD1E2"}, {"file_name": "4.png", "id": "847240705946129", "uri": "https://scontent-ams4-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031326_847240709279462_9081410908319983688_n.png?_nc_cat=107&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=_3xEQfkK1pIQ7kNvgEKzzGj&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-ams4-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDp83teFpwuMFLLKs2pJyMcGp-Q3uwPsTT5dLpg8HZIYA&oe=677BA6C2"}, {"file_name": "5.png", "id": "2404697546328669", "uri": "https://scontent-ams4-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/57572936_2404697549662002_6744001405025737672_n.png?_nc_cat=102&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=hZb9e_cRGl4Q7kNvgGqqrue&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-ams4-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAxpFUd3FzDm3GJufh8CkEVC3HsLYBEpQqajrYsvUYtQA&oe=677BD033"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "cover.png", "id": "578040073613401", "uri": "https://scontent-ams4-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39001713_578040076946734_8153214829952110504_n.png?_nc_cat=102&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=-T-Jy9Ob-kcQ7kNvgHY2s65&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-ams4-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDpVBgWxxQ5Pe9BdmNDo1xEME1u57aH8kPkmLrKOfx-4Q&oe=677BD8CE"}, "display_name": "First Person Tennis - The Real Tennis Simulator", "keywords": [], "long_description": "First Person Tennis is the first tennis simulator developed for VR.\n\nNow, you can play on a real tennis court and face professional tennis players. \nYou'll have to show all your technical and tactical skills.\n\nVR Controls:\nHold the controller/racket and play tennis.\n\nFeatures: \n- Arcade and Simulation mode.\n- Online Multiplayer.\n- 3 different ways to run through the court: Teleport, Run in Place, Sliding Run.\n- One handed serve.\n- 7 different court surfaces: clay, grass, 